entry.title: Venison Droewors: Delicious free range pet treat (100g)
entry.summary:

Type: Pet Snacks

Raw Love Venison Droewors (100 g) is made with free range organic venison which is air dried and contains no salt, grains, sugar or other additives - only delicious goodness for your pet. Perfect as a treat or a reward.

  • Contains no grains, fat, salt, sugar or other harmful additives

Use as a night time treat to relax dogs and cats!

entry.title: Cannapaw CBD Pet Treats (Certified USDA Organic Broad Spectrum CBD)
entry.summary:
Vendor: Cannapaw
Type: Pet Snacks
Price: 64.50

Cannapaw's CBD Treats are a delicious and healthy snack for your beloved pet! Organic, yummy and therapeutic CBD treats.

  • Use for training or as an anytime treat 
  • Therapeutic ingredients help relax and calm anxious, distressed or highly-strung animals (thunder, fireworks, separation, new baby etc.)
  • CBD treats help with with pain, aches and inflammation (e.g. arthritis)
  • Aids digestive health
  • Reduces allergies 
  • Inhibits cancer growth

Ingredients

Certified USDA Organic Broad Spectrum CBD, Citrus Bioflavonoids, Organic Coconut Oil, Pumpkin, Peanut Butter, Wheat Flour, Low Salt, Low Sodium Beef Stock, Potassium Sorbate (safe for animals)

Directions for use

1-2 treats depending on size. Start small (1/2 a treat) and increase if needed.
